### List NFTs of a Particular User

This endpoint will list all the NFTs that a particular user has in their wallet

### URL Parameters

| Key          | Value |
|:--------  |:-------|
| option | **onSale** or **draft** or **onAuction** or **all** |
| page | page number |

### Response

#### 200 Ok

```JSON
{
  "response": {
    "statusCode": 200,
    "message": "Success",
    "error": false,
    "version": "*.*.*"
  },
   "data": {
    "message": "NFT list",
    "list": [
      {
        "_id": "61934df7c981a91d589a4fc7",
        "name": "mountainss",
        "price": "5",
        "onSale": false,
        "onAuction": true,
        "status": "created",
        "attributes": [
          {
            "trait_type": "size",
            "value": "100x100"
          }
        ],
        "assetType": "721",
        "owner": {ownerDetails...},
        "assetId": "14"
      },
      {NFTDetails...},
      {NFTDetails...}
    ]
  }
}
```

